    </p> -->
  </p>
</div>
<div class="subtext large-offset-1 columns large-5 columns">
  <h1>SAY HI</h1>
  <p>
    We built hashtat for you and need your feedback to be better! Let us know if you found a bug, if you have ideas, or just wanna say hiya.
    <p>
      Tweet us @mrhashtat or e-mail 
        <a href="mailto:mrhashtat@gmail.com">mrhashtat@gmail.com</a>.
    </p>
  </p>
</div>
</div>
